rComments: He's great, the lectures are really interesting and Wheaton really tries to keep you engaged. You can tell he gets nervous before giving his lecture, but it doesn't really affect his teaching. You will have to study for a vocabulary test every week but if you keep on top of that, then you will do really well for the quizzes and the final exam.
